
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Sternal mass' from the dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' radio button is enabled and preselected
And 'I know' radio button is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
And 'Characterization III' tab is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' tab is enabled

And 'Sternal manubrium' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sternal body' checkbox is enabled
And 'Xiphoid process' checkbox is enabled

And 'Size' input field is enabled

And 'Cirumscribed' radio button is enabled
And 'Non-circumscribed' radio button is enabled

And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled

And 'Intact' radio button is enabled
And 'Thinning ("Scalopping")' radio button is enabled
And 'Destruction' radio button is enabled
And 'Neocorticalis' radio button is enabled

And 'Round' radio button is enabled
And 'Lobulated' radio button is enabled
And 'Geographic, map-like appearance' radio button is enabled
And 'Broad-based' radio button is enabled
And 'Pedunculated' radio button is enabled

And 'Osseous' radio button is enabled
And 'Chondroid' radio button is enabled

When I enter any value between 1 and 300 in 'Size' input field
Then '2nd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter any value between 1 and 300 in '2nd plane' input field
Then '3rd plane' input field is enabled
